<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v12" title="Q8_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p><p>
      Se prepararán vasos de té helado saborizado. La información relevante se presenta en el siguiente registro:
      <br />
      1) <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> onza = <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> mL
      <br />
      2) Cantidad por vaso (en onzas):
      <br />
      
      - Jarabe de durazno: <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>
      <br />
      - Té frío: <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>
      <br />
      3) Número de vasos a preparar: <m:math><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:math>
    </p>
    <p>
      Considerando que <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> onza equivale a <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> mL, ¿cuántos mL de jarabe de durazno se necesitan para preparar todos los vasos?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">3600 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3600</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>120</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe, pero se necesitan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>3600</m:mn></m:math> mL no alcanzan.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">10800 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Cada vaso lleva <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe. Para <m:math><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:math> vasos se necesitan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, y como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL, entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>360</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">7200 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7200</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe, pero el total requerido es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>7200</m:mn></m:math> mL es menor que lo necesario.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">21600 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>21&#160;600</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe, pero solo se requieren <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Entonces, <m:math><m:mn>21&#160;600</m:mn></m:math> mL corresponde al doble de lo necesario.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar la cantidad de jarabe por vaso</strong></p>
            <p>Cada vaso lleva <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jarabe de durazno.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular las onzas totales de jarabe para 240 vasos</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math> onzas de jarabe.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Convertir onzas a mililitros</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>360</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>10&#160;800</m:mn></m:math> mL de jarabe de durazno.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La respuesta correcta es <strong>10 800 mL</strong>, que corresponde a la <strong>alternativa B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>